Olá.

622
01:13:57,061 --> 01:13:58,229
-Bom ver você.
-Sim.

623
01:14:34,849 --> 01:14:36,017
Olá.

624
01:14:41,314 --> 01:14:42,483
Fique comigo.

625
01:14:46,528 --> 01:14:48,196
Pare, Lucy.

626
01:14:48,279 --> 01:14:50,657
Ei, olhe para mim.

627
01:14:53,535 --> 01:14:55,036
Olhe para mim.

