633
01:15:08,509 --> 01:15:09,551
Vamos lá.

634
01:15:10,343 --> 01:15:11,762
Pare com isso, Lucy.

635
01:15:13,012 --> 01:15:14,013
Vamos.

636
01:15:14,765 --> 01:15:16,224
Pare com isso, Lucy.

637
01:15:18,811 --> 01:15:19,812
Saroo!

638
01:15:20,269 --> 01:15:22,021
Você precisa
encarar a realidade.

639
01:15:23,231 --> 01:15:25,609
