<i>Saroo!</i>

657
01:18:32,921 --> 01:18:34,547
<i>Saroo!</i>

658
01:18:52,733 --> 01:18:53,692
Saroo?

659
01:18:58,989 --> 01:18:59,990
Saroo!

660
01:19:25,641 --> 01:19:27,433
